br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0f3508bd7ddfd49b760966c806572db8f9f81f87","tid":1913720,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9fdbe0b0b76558d0ba9e4282fd8089a0b9c3985","tid":1913720,"uid":555,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"成日跟下跟下唔知自己行咗去邊"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13545e85fbf4ec9ef304a56bec3934b9d3188ccc","tid":1913720,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f65ca0521d5f797465b585a7b8d1ef1556431d4d","tid":1913720,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"487b47205626d74417a623cb12144add5e3e55df","tid":1913720,"uid":1761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08525d44c2688a75bb208de9bfdfa9a369f55c24","tid":1913720,"uid":229026,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"咁其他人望到實都係因為好擔心佢地唔識保護自己, 天真傻傻唔知其他人用緊咩眼光望佢地啫.."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal